# Project Structure

This document outlines the structure of the personal portfolio website.

## Main Directories

- `src/`: Contains all source code for the application
  - `src/component/`: React components that make up the UI
  - `src/api/`: API integrations (e.g., Google Blogger API)
  - `src/stories/`: Storybook stories for component documentation
- `public/`: Static assets and HTML template
- `build/`: Production build output (generated)
- `.cursor/`: Cursor editor configuration
- `.storybook/`: Storybook configuration

## Key Files

- [src/index.js](mdc:src/index.js): Application entry point
- [src/App.js](mdc:src/App.js): Main application component with routing
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js): Tailwind CSS configuration
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project documentation

